      "text": "（いい感じだ。莉央さんの理想のイメージと）\n（莉央さんらしさが両方ともよく出てる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is good. Rio-san's ideal image）\n（and her personality are both showing well.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.9000147501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
