      "text": "……以上です。お疲れ様でした\nどれも莉央さんらしくて、いい回答ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's all. Thank you for your time.\nAll your answers were very true to yourself‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.7666814167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
