      "text": "家事の分担だって、絶対に大丈夫\n二人で力を合わせて、乗り越えてみせるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As for dividing chores‚ we'd definitely manage.\nWe'd overcome it together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.6333521524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
