      "startTime": 267.5333662746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、俺は何も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I didn't do anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.9333662746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio030.m4a",
      "text": "大体何よ、あの質問\nもし、パートナーが浮気したら……ですって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What was with that question anyway?\n\"What if your partner cheats?\" …Seriously?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.2000208535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio031.m4a",
      "text": "私が選んだパートナーは、私だけを一生\n愛してくれるの！　浮気なんて絶対しないわ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The partner I choose will love only me forever!\nThey'd never cheat!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 281.7940881809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "り、莉央さん、落ち着いて下さい。興奮し過ぎです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ calm down. You're getting too worked up.",
        "id": ""
      },
